Level Structure †

City Population = ∫Births+Immigration-Deaths-Emigration dt + [Initial population]
Initial population = 834713
    Births = City Population*Birth rate
    Deaths = City Population*Death rate
    Emigration = (City Population*Emigration rate)
    Immigration = City Population*Immigration rate*Housing availability multiplier for migration*Job availability multiplier for migration

Constructed Area[Land Use] = ∫New Constructed Area[Land Use]-Demolished Area[Land Use] dt + [Initial Constructed Area[Land Use]]
Land Use : houses, harbour, business, roads, nature, lock, railroad, canals, Flooding
    Demolished Area[Flooding] = Flooding Area Demolished
    Initial Constructed Area[Flooding] = Initial Flooding Area
    New Constructed Area[Flooding] = Planned Flooding Area

Constructed Business = ∫Business Construction-Business Demolition dt + [Initial Business]
Initial Business = 100000
    Business Construction = DELAY N( Business Planning , Delay Time business Construction , Initial Planned Business/Delay Time business Construction , Delay Order Business Construction )
    Business Demolition = Constructed Business*Demolishon Rate Business

Constructed Harbour Distribution Capacity = ∫Harbour Capacity Construction-Harbour Capacity Demolition dt + [Initial Constructed Harbour Capacity]
Initial Constructed Harbour Capacity = 200
    Harbour Capacity Construction = DELAY N( Harbour Capacity Planning , Delay Time Harbour Construction , Initial Planned Harbour Capacity/Delay Time Harbour Construction , Delay Order Harbour Construction )
    Harbour Capacity Demolition = Constructed Harbour Distribution Capacity*Demolishon Rate Harbour

Constructed Houses = ∫House Construction-House Demolition dt + [Initial Houses]
Initial Houses = 423785
    House Construction = DELAY N( House Planning , Delay Time House Construction , Initial Planned Houses/Delay Time House Construction, Delay Order House Construction )
    House Demolition = Constructed Houses*Demolishon Rate Houses

Constructed Road Capacity = ∫Renovation Road During Intervention Moment+Renovation Road During Second Intervention Moment+Road Capacity Construction-Road Capacity Detorioration-Road Capacity Diminished dt + [Initial Constructed Road Capacity]
Initial Constructed Road Capacity = Initial Number of Lanes*Initial Averaged Free Flow PCE Capacity Per Lane
    Renovation Road During Intervention Moment = PULSE(IF THEN ELSE(Switch Intervention Policy Road=0, Base Case Intervention Moment,First Intervention Moment Road System+Planning Time Renovation Road+Renovation Time Road), TIME STEP)*Cumulative Deteriorated Road Capacity/TIME STEP
    Renovation Road During Second Intervention Moment = IF THEN ELSE(Switch Intervention Policy Road=4, PULSE( Second Intervention Moment Road System+Delay Time Road Construction , TIME STEP )*Cumulative Deteriorated Road Capacity, IF THEN ELSE(Switch Intervention Policy Road=5, PULSE( Second Intervention Moment Road System+Delay Time Road Construction, TIME STEP) * Cumulative Deteriorated Road Capacity, 0))/TIME STEP
    Road Capacity Construction = DELAY FIXED (Road Capacity Planning , Delay Time Road Construction , Initial Planned Road Capacity/Delay Time Road Construction)
    Road Capacity Detorioration = ((Constructed Road Capacity*Road System Deterioration Lookup)/One Year)*(1-(IF THEN ELSE(Switch Innovation=0, Deterioration decrease Low Innovation, IF THEN ELSE(Switch Innovation=1, Deterioration decrease Mid Innovation, Deterioration decrease High Innovation))))*(1+(IF THEN ELSE(Switch Climate Scenario=0, Deterioration increase GL scenario, IF THEN ELSE(Switch Climate Scenario=1, Deterioration Increase GH scenario, Deterioration increase WL WH scenario))))
    Road Capacity Diminished = PULSE(Weakest Link Deminishing Moment, TIME STEP)*(Averaged Free Flow PCE Capacity per Lane*Number of Lanes Closed Technical end of Life)/TIME STEP

Cumulative Deteriorated Lock Capacity[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = ∫Lock Capacity Detorioration[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]-Renovating Old Locks during first intervention moment[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]-Renovating Old Locks during second intervention moment[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] dt + [Initial Cumulative Deteriorated Lock Capacity]
Initial Cumulative Deteriorated Lock Capacity = 0
    Lock Capacity Detorioration[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = ((Lock Constructed Distribution Capacity[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]*Lock System Detoriation Lookup)/One Year)*(1-(IF THEN ELSE(Switch Climate Scenario=0, Lock System Deterioration GL Scenario, IF THEN ELSE(Switch Climate Scenario=1, Lock System Deterioration GH Scenario, IF THEN ELSE(Switch Climate Scenario=2, Lock System Deterioration WL Scenario, Lock System Deterioration WH Scenario)))))
    Renovating Old Locks during first intervention moment[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = PULSE((New Lock Intervention Moments[Lock 2]+Delay Time New Lock Construction[Lock 2]),TIME STEP)*(Cumulative Deteriorated Lock Capacity[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis])/TIME STEP
    Renovating Old Locks during second intervention moment[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = PULSE((New Lock Intervention Moments[Lock 3]+Delay Time New Lock Construction[Lock 3]),TIME STEP)*(Cumulative Deteriorated Lock Capacity[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis])/TIME STEP

Cumulative Deteriorated Road Capacity = ∫Road Capacity Detorioration-Renovation Road During Intervention Moment-Renovation Road During Second Intervention Moment dt + [Initial Deteriorated Road Capacity]
Initial Deteriorated Road Capacity = 0

Cumulative Diminished Road Capacity = ∫Road Capacity Diminished dt + [Initial Diminshed Road Capacity]
Initial Diminshed Road Capacity = 0

Door Height Intervention Moment Memory = ∫Door Height Intervention Moment In-Door Height Intervention Moment Out dt + [Initial Door Height Intervention Moment Memory]
Initial Door Height Intervention Moment Memory = 0
    Door Height Intervention Moment In = IF THEN ELSE((Minimum Height Required for Doors/One Centimeter)>(MIN( Height door Old Middensluis, Height door Old Noordersluis)/One Centimeter), Time, 0)/One Year
    Door Height Intervention Moment Out = DELAY FIXED (Door Height Intervention Moment In, TIME STEP*Scaling Factor for EMA Simulation, Initial Door Height Intervention Moment Memory/One Year)

Free Area = ∫∑(Demolished Area[Land Use!])-SUM(New Constructed Area[Land Use!]) dt + [Initial Free Area]
Initial Free Area = 25000

IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment Memory = ∫IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment IN-IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment OUT dt + [Initial IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment Memory]
Initial IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment Memory = 0
    IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment IN = IF THEN ELSE(Lock System IC Factor>IC Lock Decision Making Factor, Time, 0)/One Year
    IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment OUT = DELAY FIXED (IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment IN, TIME STEP*Scaling Factor for EMA Simulation, Initial IC Factor Lock Intervention Moment Memory/One Year)

IC Factor Road Intervention Moment Memory = ∫IC Factor Road Intervention Moment IN-IC Factor Road Intervention Moment OUT dt + [Initial IC Factor Road Intervention Moment Memory]
Initial IC Factor Road Intervention Moment Memory = 0
    IC Factor Road Intervention Moment IN = IF THEN ELSE(Road System IC Factor>IC Decision Making Factor Road, Time, 0)/One Year
    IC Factor Road Intervention Moment OUT = DELAY FIXED (IC Factor Road Intervention Moment IN, (TIME STEP*Scaling Factor for EMA Simulation), Initial IC Factor Road Intervention Moment Memory/One Year)

Intervention Moment Sewer Memory = ∫Intervention Moment Sewer IN-Intervention Moment Sewer OUT dt + [Initial Intervention Moment Sewer]
Initial Intervention Moment Sewer = 0
    Intervention Moment Sewer IN = IF THEN ELSE(Maximum Precipitaiton over Road System Area>Total Sewer System Maximum Capacity, Time, 0)/One Year
    Intervention Moment Sewer OUT = DELAY FIXED (Intervention Moment Sewer IN, TIME STEP*Scaling Factor for EMA Simulation, Initial Intervention Moment Sewer/One Year)

Local Economy = ∫Micro Economic Growth dt + [Initial Local Economy]
Initial Local Economy = 6.2e+010
    Micro Economic Growth = Local Economy*(Macro Economic Growth influencing local economy+Micro Economic Growth Businesses+Micro Economic Growth Job Spenditure+Micro Economic growth Harbour)

Lock Constructed Distribution Capacity[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = ∫Lock Capacity Construction[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]-Lock Capacity Demolition[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]-Lock Capacity Detorioration[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]+Renovating Old Locks during first intervention moment[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]+Renovating Old Locks during second intervention moment[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] dt + [Initial Capacity Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]
Initial Capacity Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis = 8.333
    Lock Capacity Construction[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = 0
    Lock Capacity Demolition[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = Lock Constructed Distribution Capacity[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]*Demolishing Rate New Locks

Lock Constructed Distribution Capacity for Scaling Benefits[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = ∫Lock Capacity Construction[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]-Lock Capacity Demolition[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] dt + [Initial Capacity Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]

Part Business in Economy = ∫Growth business in economy dt + [Initial Local Economy*Initial Shares Business]
Initial Shares Business = 0.25
    Growth business in economy = Part Business in Economy*Relative Business Growth

Part Harbour in Economy = ∫Growth harbour in Economy dt + [Initial Local Economy*Initial Shares Harbour]
Initial Shares Harbour = 0.25
    Growth harbour in Economy = Part Harbour in Economy*Relative Harbour Growth

Part Job Spending in Economy = ∫Growth Job Spending dt + [Initial Local Economy*Initial Shares Job Spending]
Initial Shares Job Spending = 0.25
    Growth Job Spending = Part Job Spending in Economy * Relative Population Growth*Percentage of Labour Population actively wanting a job

Planned Business = ∫Business Planning-Business Construction dt + [Initial Planned Business]
Initial Planned Business = 1000
    Business Planning = MIN(New Planned Business, (Available Area/Land use per business)/One Year)

Planned Capacity Lock[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = ∫Capacity Planning Lock[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis]-Lock Capacity Construction[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] dt + [Initial Planned Lock Capacity]
Initial Planned Lock Capacity = 0
    Capacity Planning Lock[Old Kleine Sluis and Zuidersluis] = 0

Planned Harbour Capacity = ∫Harbour Capacity Planning-Harbour Capacity Construction dt + [Initial Planned Harbour Capacity]
Initial Planned Harbour Capacity = 50
    Harbour Capacity Planning = MIN((Available Area/MTPA to Area Factor Harbour), New Planned Harbour Capacity)/One Year

Planned Houses = ∫House Planning-House Construction dt + [Initial Planned Houses]
Initial Planned Houses = 5000
    House Planning = MIN(New Planned Houses, Available Area/Land use per house)/One Year

Planned Road Capacity = ∫Road Capacity Planning-Road Capacity Construction dt + [Initial Planned Road Capacity]
Initial Planned Road Capacity = 0
    Road Capacity Planning = New Road Capacity Planned

Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment Memory = ∫Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment In-Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment Out dt + [Initial Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment Memory]
Initial Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment Memory = 0
    Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment In = IF THEN ELSE((Minimum Height required for remaining parts lock/One Centimeter)>(Minimum present Height of remaining parts/One Centimeter), Time, 0)/One Year
    Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment Out = DELAY FIXED (Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment In,TIME STEP*Scaling Factor for EMA Simulation, Initial Remaining Parts Height Intervention Moment Memory/One Year)

Sewer System Maximum Capacity = ∫Increased Sewer Capacity dt + [Initial Sewer System Maximum Capacity]
Initial Sewer System Maximum Capacity = 45
    Increased Sewer Capacity = PULSE(IF THEN ELSE(Switch Intervention Policy Road=0, Intervention Moment Road System, IF THEN ELSE(Switch Intervention Policy Road=4, First Intervention Moment Road System+Renovation Time Road+Planning Time Renovation Road, IF THEN ELSE(Switch Intervention Policy Road=5, First Intervention Moment Road System+Planning Time Renovation Road+Renovation Time Road, Intervention Moment Road System+Delay Time Road Construction))), TIME STEP)*(IF THEN ELSE(Switch Sewer Intervention=0, 0, Sewer Capacity increased After Intervention)/TIME STEP)

World Offer MTPA[Canal] = ∫World Offer MTPA Growth[Canal] dt + [Initial World Offer MTPA[Canal]]
    Initial World Offer MTPA[Canal] = Initial world offer canal MTPA
    World Offer MTPA Growth[Flow Type] = World Offer MTPA[Flow Type]*Macro Economic Growth

†  Level Structure Report still under development.
